cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.CE, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.AI - The paper proposes an expert system which uses decision trees to automate the process of employing lecturers. This falls under the domain of artificial intelligence. 
2. cs.LG - The proposed system uses machine learning methods to extract rules from decision trees. This falls under the domain of machine learning. 
3. cs.SE - The paper discusses the development of a software system to help the head of university departments. This falls under the domain of software engineering. 
4. cs.CE - The paper discusses the design and development of an automated system using expert systems. This falls under the domain of computer engineering. 
5. cs.IR - The paper discusses the use of a majority voting algorithm to improve the quality of the proposed system. This falls under the domain of information retrieval.
